'''Byron Bertram''' (born October 29, 1952, in [[Johannesburg, South Africa]]), is a former professional [[tennis]] player from South Africa, where he attended [[Parktown Boys' High School]].  He enjoyed most of his tennis success while playing doubles.  During his career he won 1 doubles title.

